<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title> {{ title }} </title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/{{style}}.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="search-container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-12">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-center">
                        <input type="text" id="repoInput" class="form-control search-input flex-grow-1" 
                               placeholder="Paste GitHub repository URL here (e.g., https://github.com/user/repo)">
                        <button id="searchBtn" class="btn search-btn">
                            <span class="btn-text">Analyze</span>
                            <div class="loading">
                                <div class="spinner-border spinner-border-sm" role="status"></div>
                            </div>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center mt-4">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <h2 id="repoTitle" class="repo-title"></h2>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="cards-container">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row g-4">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12">
                        <div class="card info-card">
                            <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                                <div class="card-icon">üìå</div>
                                <h5 class="card-title">Where can I start?</h5>
                                <div id="startContent" class="card-content">
                                    <p>Discover beginner-friendly issues and good first contributions. We'll analyze the repository to find tasks marked as "good first issue", "help wanted", or similar beginner-friendly labels.</p>
                                    <div class="text-muted small">Enter a repository URL above to get started</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12">
                        <div class="card info-card">
                            <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                                <div class="card-icon">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
                                <h5 class="card-title">What needs improving?</h5>
                                <div id="improvingContent" class="card-content">
                                    <p>Identify areas that need attention - missing documentation, outdated README files, stale branches, or code that could benefit from refactoring.</p>
                                    <div class="text-muted small">Analysis will appear here after searching</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12">
                        <div class="card info-card">
                            <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                                <div class="card-icon">üìÉ</div>
                                <h5 class="card-title">What rules should I follow?</h5>
                                <div id="rulesContent" class="card-content">
                                    <p>Learn about the project's contribution guidelines, code of conduct, coding standards, and development workflow from CONTRIBUTING.md and other policy files.</p>
                                    <div class="text-muted small">Guidelines will be summarized here</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12">
                        <div class="card info-card">
                            <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                                <div class="card-icon">üîé</div>
                                <h5 class="card-title">What's this repo about?</h5>
                                <div id="aboutContent" class="card-content">
                                    <p>Get an AI-generated summary of the project's purpose, main features, technology stack, and overall architecture to understand what you'll be working with.</p>
                                    <div class="text-muted small">Project summary will appear here</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/{{script}}.js"></script>
</body>
</html>